properties.name: Guid
properties.description: The **Guid** is an object used to generate and contain a GUID.

Methods.name: ctor()
Methods.description: Creates a new **Guid** instance that contains a generated GUID.

Methods.name: ctor(value)
Methods.description: Creates a new **Guid** instance that contains the specified GUID.

Methods.name: toString()
Methods.description: Gets the GUID. Works identically to the [valueOf()].md '/Documentation/ApiReference/Data_Layer/Guid/Methods/#valueOf') method.

Methods.name: valueOf()
Methods.description: Gets the GUID. Works identically to the [toString()].md '/Documentation/ApiReference/Data_Layer/Guid/Methods/#toString') method.
